						               													<description>The game is comprised of a Game Board, eight colored &amp;quot;Spools of Thread&amp;quot; (which are the game playing pieces), a single die (to control game flow), 3,000 quilting and sewing trivia &amp;quot;Question / Answer Cards&amp;quot; (6 questions and answers per card with a total of 500 cards, click on the Sample Questions spool to the left for an example, there are 1,000 questions and they change daily, 3 new questions per day so come back each day and test your knowledge), and 200 &amp;quot;Perk&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;Quirk&amp;quot; cards which bestow benefits or penalties respectively.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of the game is to visit each of the four quilt stores located on the game board (Barnyard Quilts, Heavenly Quiltworks, Windmill Quilts and Riverview Quilts), as well as an additional number of locations decided upon by the game players.  The duration of the game can be lengthened or shortened depending on the total number of locations that the players decide must be visited, however, at a minimum the players must visit all four of the quilt stores to win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Home Page: http://www.sewyouwanttobeaquilter.com&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
